      "content": "命名维度：type/size/variant/shape/state\ntype= Button、Input、SearchBox\n\nsize= Medium （32） Large （40）\nvariant= Neutra White\nstate= Default Hover Click Loading Disabled Focus Inputing\n\n对应到按钮 type=Input\nSearchBox/White/Medium/Default\nSearchBox/White/Medium/Hover\nSearchBox/White/Medium/Focus\nSearchBox/White/Medium/Inputing\n\nData Entry 待添加\n基本用法☑️\n校验用法\n前缀&后缀输入框\n提示文案用法\n后缀「清除」图标 输入框\n后缀（下拉）图标输入框"
    },
